l rushed, they hold your bag out to you, making sure you know that the entire time it takes you to put your change away -- the person behind you has to wait.  You can't just step aside while you fumble around, no, you have to make the entire line wait for you.<br><br>Then, go ahead, put the receipt in with the bills, so you have to separate that out -- no one puts receipts in their wallet, after all.  So now you have bills, coins, with receipt on the top of it all.<br><br>And of course, the obligatory bag for the one book -- the bag that's just going to get thrown away.<br><br>---<br><br>Please, someone explain this to me.<br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f7f7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub95.ezboard.com/uvaeluudar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Vaeluudar</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://publish.hometown.aol.com/slytlidisturbed/images/thev.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Indifferent Poster</span><br> <font color=#778899>(1/19/02 10:02:16 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/finnoruukserverfrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=362.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://publish.hometown.aol.com/slytlidisturbed/images/thev.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: OOC Rant: Cashiers</span><hr size=1> Theyre out to get you man. <p><br><br><p><img src="http://publish.hometown.aol.com/slytlidisturbed/images/vaeluudar.jpg"></p><p align="center"><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=60323">Vaeluudar's Profile</a></p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f7f7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub95.ezboard.com/uunilove.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Unilove</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_redspot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Threatening Poster</span><br> <font